Frequently Asked Questions

What is online homoeopathic treatment?
Online homoeopathy treatment means receiving professional homoeopathic consultation and medicines delivered right to your doorstep, anywhere in India or abroad. Modern technology like email, phone consultations, and video calls allow us to conduct thorough case analysis without requiring you to visit the clinic in person.
How can treatment be effective without seeing the patient?
Classical homoeopathy relies heavily on understanding the patient's complete symptom picture, medical history, mental and emotional state, and lifestyle. All of this information can be effectively gathered through detailed case forms, phone/video consultations, and email communication. Modern facilities make it possible to conduct comprehensive consultations remotely.
What conditions can be treated with homoeopathy?
Homoeopathy is effective for both acute and chronic conditions including joint disorders, skin problems, allergies, respiratory issues, digestive disorders, women's health problems, stress and anxiety, pediatric conditions, and many more. Consultation will help determine if homoeopathy is suitable for your specific condition.
How long does treatment take?
Treatment duration varies based on the nature and severity of the condition. Acute conditions may respond quickly within days or weeks, while chronic conditions typically require 2-6 months or longer. Dr. Jaiswal will provide a realistic timeframe during your consultation based on your specific case.
Are there any side effects?
Homoeopathic medicines are prepared from natural substances in highly diluted forms and are completely safe with no side effects. They are gentle, non-toxic, and can be safely used by people of all ages including infants, pregnant women, and elderly patients.
